covery-that-hunter-gatherer-children-died-of-plague-more-than-five-millennia-ago-sets-back-the-date-of-the-earliest-outbreak-180988983/</guid></item><item><title>与罗宾汉传说有关的 1,200 岁树大橡树因无法长出叶子而被推定死亡</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/major-oak-the-1200-year-old-tree-with-ties-to-the-robin-hood-legend-is-presumed-dead-after-failing-to-produce-leaves-180988986/</link><description>据说，传说中的强盗从富人那里偷东西给穷人，在躲避诺丁汉警长的追捕时，用这棵大树作为藏身之处。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 20:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/major-oak-the-1200-year-old-tree-with-ties-to-the-robin-hood-legend-is-presumed-dead-after-failing-to-produce-leaves-180988986/</guid></item><item><title>这家摄影工作室捕捉了南方黑人生活的美丽。很快，曾经隐藏起来的档案馆将拥有一个新的博物馆所在地</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-photography-studio-hooks-brothers-captured-the-beauty-of-black-life-in-the-south-soon-its-archive-once-hidden-away-will-have-a-new-museum-home-180988982/</link><description>胡克斯兄弟记录了 20 世纪孟菲斯的生活和欢乐。他们的照片将在孟菲斯艺术博物馆开放时向公众展示</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 19:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-photography-studio-hooks-brothers-captured-the-beauty-of-black-life-in-the-south-soon-its-archive-once-hidden-away-will-have-a-new-museum-home-180988982/</guid></item><item><title>天文学家通过回望时间的边缘，发现了正在形成的“宇宙化石”——迄今为止所见过的化学性质最原始的星系</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/astronomers-discovered-a-cosmic-fossil-in-the-making-the-most-chemically-primitive-galaxy-seen-yet-by-peering-back-to-the-edge-of-time-180988954/</link><description>詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜使用像放大镜一样的较近的星系团观察了 130 亿年前的光。这项工作帮助专家了解宇宙中最早的恒星和神秘的超微弱矮星系</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 16:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/astronomers-discovered-a-cosmic-fossil-in-the-making-the-most-chemically-primitive-galaxy-seen-yet-by-peering-back-to-the-edge-of-time-180988954/</guid></item><item>